title: Crime Investigation Australia - Season 3
description:
Crime Investigation Australia - Season 3

Crime Investigation Australia includes heartbreaking interviews from victims, loved ones and the investigators who brought the criminals to justice. These horrific crimes are brought to life in dramatic re-enactments shot in the actual locations the crimes took place. What makes a serial killer tick? How do forensic experts solve crimes using cutting edge technology? Who are the men and women that risk their lives to put criminals behind bars? These questions and more are answered.

Ep 1 - The Girls Who Knew Too Much
Ep 2 - Bloodsport-The Bondi Gay Murders
Ep 3 - A Killer Amongst Us-The Norfolk Island Murder
Ep 4 - Night Of Terror-The Bega Schoolgirls
Ep 5 - Murder Of Innocence-Sian Kingi
Ep 6 - Date With A Serial Killer-Rodney Cameron
Ep 7 - Cop Killer-The Winchester Assassination
Ep 8 - Michael Kanaan-Shoot To Kill
Ep 9 - Buried Alive-Luckman & Reid
Ep 10 - Mystery Of The Homestead Murders
